<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | AI Diary</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/404.css">
   
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="diary-icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open-reader"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="error-number">404</div>
        
        <h1 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h1>
        
        <p class="error-subtitle">
            Oops! It seems like this page has disappeared into the digital void. 
            <br>Don't worry, let's get you back to documenting your thoughts and memories.
        </p>
        
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/" class="btn-primary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Back to Home
            </a>
            <a href="/login" class="btn-secondary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>Login
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="suggestions">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-2"></i>Quick Navigation</h3>
            <ul class="suggestion-list">
                <li><a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Homepage</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>Login to Your Diary</a></li>
                <li><a href="/register"><i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i>Create New Account</a></li>
                <li><a href="/diary/new"><i class="fas fa-plus me-2"></i>Write New Entry</a></li>
                <li><a href="/diary/analytics"><i class="fas fa-chart-line me-2"></i>View Analytics</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/" class="brand-link">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open-reader"></i>
            <span>AI Diary</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ndDqU0Gzau9qJ1lfW4pNLlhNTkCfHzAVBReH9diLlhNTkCfHzAVBReH9diLvGRem5+R9g2FzA8ZGN954O5Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>